000100 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000200 PROGRAM-ID. CONTROL.
000300*
000400 DATA DIVISION.
000500 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
000600 01  WS-NUM          PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.
000700 01  WS-MSG          PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
000800*
000900 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
001000 MAIN-PARA.
001100     MOVE 5 TO WS-NUM.
001200     IF WS-NUM > 3
001300         MOVE "GREATER THAN 3" TO WS-MSG
001400     ELSE
001500         MOVE "NOT GREATER" TO WS-MSG
001600     END-IF.
001700     DISPLAY WS-MSG.
001800*
001900     EVALUATE WS-NUM
002000         WHEN 1
002100             DISPLAY "ONE"
002200         WHEN 2
002300             DISPLAY "TWO"
002400         WHEN 5
002500             DISPLAY "FIVE"
002600         WHEN OTHER
002700             DISPLAY "OTHER"
002800     END-EVALUATE.
002900*
003000     PERFORM PRINT-PARA.
003100*
003200     MOVE 1 TO WS-NUM.
003300     PERFORM COUNT-PARA UNTIL WS-NUM > 10.
003400*
003500     GO TO END-PARA.
003600*
003700 PRINT-PARA.
003800     DISPLAY "PERFORMED PRINT-PARA".
003900*
004000 COUNT-PARA.
004100     DISPLAY "COUNT: " WS-NUM.
004200     ADD 1 TO WS-NUM.
004300*
004400 END-PARA.
004500     STOP RUN.
